phpbiff has the following dependencies:
 - >=PHP 5.2.12 with the filter, hash, mcrypt, and sockets modules installed and
   enabled.
 - >=mcrypt-2.6.7 (for the PHP mcrypt module.)
 - A server filesystem that supports flock.
   (i.e. not older Windows FAT filesystems.)

PEAR-PhpDocumentor-1.4.1 was used to generate the API documentation.

PHPUnit-3.3.1 is used for the unit tests.
